Invocation Name: daily math fact
des:
Ask for Math Facts, and learn about many different math facts.

Plus you provides fun family and friends can enjoy and is guaranteed to make you smarter.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch daily math fact" or "Alexa, open daily math fact" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
